Salaam.

14:29.956 --> 14:31.348
How's the Christmas?

14:31.392 --> 14:35.004
Oh, it is wonderful
and magical, and...

14:35.048 --> 14:38.529
It is crazy.
Everyone is fighting.

14:38.573 --> 14:39.922
So, it's not like
in the movies?

14:39.966 --> 14:42.577
No, except for maybe
Die Hard.

14:45.928 --> 14:49.236
So how long have you
and my dad been... friends?

14:49.279 --> 14:51.107
We've been friends
for a couple of years,

14:51.151 --> 14:54.763
and "friends" for about a week.

14:56.852 --> 14:58.288
Oh. Hey!

14:58.332 --> 15:01.639
We out here playing basketball
or Barbies?

15:01.683 --> 15:04.425
Okay, I see you.

15:05.992 --> 15:08.255
So, what's the plan
with you guys?

15:08.298 --> 15:11.388
Man, you really drive
to the basket, don't you?

15:11.432 --> 15:12.781
I'm just trying to figure out

15:12.824 --> 15:14.870
whether it's worth
learning your last name.

15:17.351 --> 15:20.658
Beat me to 11,
maybe I'll tell you.

15:22.791 --> 15:24.488
Come on. Come on.

15:30.320 --> 15:31.495
Hey.

15:31.539 --> 15:33.280
Hey.

15:33.323 --> 15:35.935
Your party's going great.

15:35.978 --> 15:38.981
I mean, it's usually not the
host who leaves early, but...

15:43.725 --> 15:45.466
I don't know
what to tell you.

15:46.641 --> 15:48.121
I'm a simple guy.

15:48.164 --> 15:50.775
With a lot of opinions.[sighs]

15:50.819 --> 15:53.865
It's just who I am,
and I'm too old to change.

15:53.909 --> 15:55.476
[chuckles]

15:55.519 --> 15:56.999
I don't mind
that you have money.

15:57.043 --> 15:59.001
Y-You obviously do.

15:59.045 --> 16:01.351
But I earned it, and
I want to spend it

16:01.395 --> 16:04.485
on things that make
me happy, which was you

16:04.528 --> 16:07.357
until two hours ago.

16:10.317 --> 16:12.536
So, what do we do?

16:12.580 --> 16:16.323
Well, first, you
apologize for being rude.

16:16.366 --> 16:18.499
