16:21.893 --> 16:24.200
I am so sorry.

16:25.245 --> 16:29.379
And you don't get to make me
feel bad for the choices I make.

16:30.380 --> 16:32.904
So, you want me
to get my head around the fact

16:32.948 --> 16:37.300
that you're rich
and sexy and generous?

16:37.344 --> 16:39.955
I'll give it a shot.

16:40.956 --> 16:43.002
You're very brave.

16:44.351 --> 16:46.657
And next year,

16:46.701 --> 16:49.182
I'll give you
those socket wrenches.

16:49.225 --> 16:53.012
Next year? I like
the sound of that.

16:59.714 --> 17:01.759
Want to stick around
for the after-party?

17:01.803 --> 17:03.935
You gonna wear the sweater?

17:03.979 --> 17:05.154
That's all I'm gonna wear.

17:05.198 --> 17:07.200
[laughs]

17:13.728 --> 17:17.079
Hey. What are you doing in here?

17:17.123 --> 17:19.603
I drank too much.

17:20.909 --> 17:22.606
Where's your girlfriend?

17:22.650 --> 17:26.262
She went home.
Where's your boyfriend?

17:26.306 --> 17:28.395
He went home.

17:29.396 --> 17:31.528
Everyone's pissed at me.

17:31.572 --> 17:33.617
What did I do?

17:33.661 --> 17:36.359
[sighs]
Well...

17:36.403 --> 17:40.624
you are half in the bag and were
rude to everyone at the party.

17:40.668 --> 17:43.932
Kind of stole
my move there.

17:43.975 --> 17:46.195
I put up with so much from you.

17:46.239 --> 17:49.459
You were a mess for years,
and you cheated on me.

17:49.503 --> 17:51.461
You refused to get help.

17:51.505 --> 17:53.898
I'm so mad.

17:53.942 --> 17:55.074
[sighs]

17:55.117 --> 17:56.901
You're right.

17:56.945 --> 18:01.080
I'm sorry. I really am,
and I'm working on it.

18:01.123 --> 18:05.432
If you get better, and then
she gets you, how is that fair?

18:05.475 --> 18:07.651
Where is that coming from?

18:07.695 --> 18:09.784
I don't know.

18:12.656 --> 18:13.918
