18:13.962 --> 18:16.443
you want
to give us another chance?

18:17.444 --> 18:18.793
I don't know.

18:21.012 --> 18:22.666
Oh, God.

18:22.710 --> 18:25.060
I hate being the messy one.

18:28.542 --> 18:31.153
